<h1>Welcome to CFP.sh</h1>

<h2>Your Community Hub for Tech Conference CFPs</h2>

<p>At CFP.sh, we're committed to empowering speakers and fostering a vibrant tech conference ecosystem. Our mission is to provide resources, support, and a platform for community engagement around Call for Papers (CFPs) for technology conferences.</p>

<h3>What We Offer</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>CFP Writing Guide</strong>: Comprehensive resources to help you craft compelling proposals</li>
  <li><strong>Conference List</strong>: Up-to-date directory of tech conferences and their CFP deadlines</li>
  <li><strong>Community Forum</strong>: A space for speakers to connect, share experiences, and seek advice</li>
  <li><strong>Resource Library</strong>: Curated tools and tips to enhance your speaking journey</li>
</ul>

<h2>Get Involved</h2>

<p>We believe in the power of community. Here's how you can contribute:</p>

<ol>
  <li><strong>Share Your Expertise</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Submit guest posts on CFP writing tips</li>
      <li>Offer to mentor new speakers</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Contribute to Our Resources</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Help maintain our conference list</li>
      <li>Suggest improvements to our guides</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Engage in Discussions</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Participate in our community forum</li>
      <li>Join our monthly virtual meetups</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Spread the Word</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Share cfp.sh with your network</li>
      <li>Follow us on social media <a href="https://x.com/cfp_sh">@cfp_sh</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

